{"tid":360673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣大停電 經濟部長問責即時請辭","createTime":"2017-08-15T13:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T14:43:57.000Z","uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c699446b6af9160ebdd6bb4461865da7d59d43fb","tid":360673,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/politics/20170815/1183064/%E8%B7%B3%E9%9B%BB%E7%A9%B6%E8%B2%AC%E3%80%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E6%9D%8E%E4%B8%96%E5%85%89%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2F20170815%2F1183064%2F%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2587%2586&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1a349438\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/politics/20170815/1183064/%E8%B7%B3%E9%9B%BB%E7%A9%B6%E8%B2%AC%E3%80%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E6%9D%8E%E4%B8%96%E5%85%89%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170815/420_1ffc95d72f110a10ff49e3d917718bfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170815%2F420_1ffc95d72f110a10ff49e3d917718bfb.jpg&h=3c604800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（更新：新增林全臉書內容）<br />\n<br />\n全台大跳電，民怨四起！桃園大潭電廠機組在今傍晚近5時全數跳脫，電力頓失438.4萬瓩，造成全台陸續停電，經濟部長李世光稍早舉行記者會時強調，該負的政治責任完全不會閃躲。行政院發言人徐國勇晚間表示，李世光已經向院長林全口頭請辭，林全也已經接受。<br />\n<br />\n針對國民黨立院黨團要求政院在臨時會進行專案報告，徐國勇也說，尊重立院，只要立院做出決議，要求政院報告，就會前往立法院報告。<br />\n<br />\n林全稍晚也透過臉書表示，針對全台17縣市停電事件，向因跳電造成不便的全國民眾道歉。<br />\n<br />\n林全強調，經濟部、台電與中油公司已召開記者會作初步說明，他也要求經濟部必須查明原因，並且追究相關人員的責任。針對台電今晚將採行緊急分區輪流限電，預計會有部分用戶受影響。林全已請台電在最短的時間內恢復供電，減少民眾因停電帶來的不便。（陳雅芃／台北報導）"},{"pid":"b38ac24d47571455fa28d5da164569eecec1d6b9","tid":360673,"uid":52595,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8637c8396d2168467a4e0e21edba6c29af8a2c99","tid":360673,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵成日壞車，邊個需要請辭？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賺到錢就ok了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8259498c67f1648981aa99c8b9eeeb3150b2f817","tid":360673,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"大交合令全港打工仔冒生命危險返工<br />\n台長係咪應該請辭"},{"pid":"61f7d1d53b1875802221502defc8bcc2fa5d1d5a","tid":360673,"uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"請辭 其實係一個不負責任既行為<br />\n<br />\n你做錯事, 跟住拍拍羅友走人??<br />\n<br />\n最應該係繼續留低, 改番自己既過失"},{"pid":"d82f6f602591ed5ee710ff72db390f912564975b","tid":360673,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"佢有咩錯"},{"pid":"ffdfa4c780c3edf7659d596c4984e32975f0221d","tid":360673,"uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有咩錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中油出錯 部長負責"},{"pid":"6507e75b5075d730a609615c21760d48eecc471c","tid":360673,"uid":45232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢有咩錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中油出錯 部長負責</blockquote><br />\n因為一個小員工出錯 全國停電<br />\n即係本身成個系統有問題喇"},{"pid":"03b0c9a518ef586ad99ebac2a809367739d3c7c8","tid":360673,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0